{
  "page": "Feature quote/178",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“The <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">crannogman</a> saw a <a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">maid with laughing purple eyes</a> dance with a <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">white sword</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">red snake</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">lord of griffins</a>, and lastly with the <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">quiet wolf</a> . . . but only after the <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">wild wolf</a> spoke to her on behalf of a brother too shy to leave his bench.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404115539\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 124/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 300/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expa